template.name: Email Campaign
template.desc: Upload Excel file, fill out the form using the variables from your excel file plus your custmized content and send emails to a list of people

flow.name: Email Campaign Flow
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI">
    <process id="emailCampaignFlow" name="Email Campaign Flow" isExecutable="true">
        <startEvent id="startevent1" name="Start"/>
        <endEvent id="endevent1" name="End"/>
        <subProcess id="subprocess1" name="Sub Process">
            <multiInstanceLoopCharacteristics isSequential="false" activiti:collection="targetArrayList" activiti:elementVariable="targetElement"/>
            <scriptTask id="scripttask1" name="Script Task" scriptFormat="groovy" activiti:autoStoreVariables="false">
                <script>//******************* check list of auditor for review for end date within 5 days  *****
package processes.scripts
import groovy.json.*

def email_e = targetElement.to.replaceAll('var_one', targetElement.var_one).replaceAll('var_two', targetElement.var_two).replaceAll('var_three', targetElement.var_three).replaceAll('var_four', targetElement.var_four).replaceAll('var_five', targetElement.var_five).replaceAll('var_six', targetElement.var_six).replaceAll('var_seven', targetElement.var_seven)
def subject_s = targetElement.subject.replaceAll('var_one', targetElement.var_one).replaceAll('var_two', targetElement.var_two).replaceAll('var_three', targetElement.var_three).replaceAll('var_four', targetElement.var_four).replaceAll('var_five', targetElement.var_five).replaceAll('var_six', targetElement.var_six).replaceAll('var_seven', targetElement.var_seven)
def content_c = targetElement.body.replaceAll('var_one', targetElement.var_one).replaceAll('var_two', targetElement.var_two).replaceAll('var_three', targetElement.var_three).replaceAll('var_four', targetElement.var_four).replaceAll('var_five', targetElement.var_five).replaceAll('var_six', targetElement.var_six).replaceAll('var_seven', targetElement.var_seven)

execution.setVariable('emailTo', email_e)
execution.setVariable('emailSubject', subject_s)
execution.setVariable('emailContent', content_c)
</script>
            </scriptTask>
            <sequenceFlow id="flow10" sourceRef="scripttask1" targetRef="notificationFact"/>
            <serviceTask id="notificationFact" name="Notification Fact" activiti:type="mail">
                <extensionElements>
                    <activiti:field name="subject">
                        <activiti:expression>${emailSubject}</activiti:expression>
                    </activiti:field>
                    <activiti:field name="html">
                        <activiti:expression>${emailContent}</activiti:expression>
                    </activiti:field>
                    <activiti:field name="to">
                        <activiti:expression>${emailTo}</activiti:expression>
                    </activiti:field>
                    <activiti:field name="from">
                        <activiti:string>alert@point.io</activiti:string>
                    </activiti:field>
                </extensionElements>
            </serviceTask>
            <sequenceFlow id="flow8" sourceRef="notificationFact" targetRef="endevent2"/>
            <endEvent id="endevent2" name="End"/>
            <startEvent id="startevent2" name="Start"/>
            <sequenceFlow id="flow11" sourceRef="startevent2" targetRef="scripttask1"/>
        </subProcess>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow12" sourceRef="subprocess1" targetRef="endevent1"/>
        <scriptTask id="scripttask2" name="Script Task" scriptFormat="groovy" activiti:autoStoreVariables="false">
            <script>//******************* check list of auditor for review for end date within 5 days  *****
package processes.scripts
import groovy.json.*
def jsonSlurperClassic = new JsonSlurperClassic()
def myArray_s = new java.util.ArrayList();

targetGroovyJson = new groovy.json.JsonBuilder(jsonSlurperClassic.parseText(execution.getVariable('target')))

targetGroovyJson.content.each {aTarget ->
	myArray_s.add(aTarget);	
}
execution.setVariable('targetArrayList', myArray_s );</script>
        </scriptTask>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow13" sourceRef="scripttask2" targetRef="subprocess1"/>
        <userTask id="usertask1" name="Build Data" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" activiti:formKey="poi_buildData_form"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow14" sourceRef="startevent1" targetRef="usertask1"/>
        <sequenceFlow id="flow15" sourceRef="usertask1" targetRef="scripttask2"/>
    </process>
    <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_emailCampaignFlow">
        <bpmndi:BPMNPlane bpmnElement="emailCampaignFlow" id="BPMNPlane_emailCampaignFlow">
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="startevent1" id="BPMNShape_startevent1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="0.0" y="180.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="endevent1" id="BPMNShape_endevent1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="810.0" y="180.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="subprocess1" id="BPMNShape_subprocess1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="205.0" width="481.0" x="270.0" y="120.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="scripttask1" id="BPMNShape_scripttask1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="400.0" y="170.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="notificationFact" id="BPMNShape_notificationFact">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="540.0" y="170.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="endevent2" id="BPMNShape_endevent2">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="700.0" y="180.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="startevent2" id="BPMNShape_startevent2">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="35.0" width="35.0" x="310.0" y="180.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="scripttask2" id="BPMNShape_scripttask2">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="45.0" y="310.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNShape bpmnElement="usertask1" id="BPMNShape_usertask1">
                <omgdc:Bounds height="55.0" width="105.0" x="85.0" y="176.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNShape>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow10" id="BPMNEdge_flow10">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="505.0" y="197.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="540.0" y="197.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow8" id="BPMNEdge_flow8">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="645.0" y="197.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="700.0" y="197.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow11" id="BPMNEdge_flow11">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="345.0" y="197.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="400.0" y="197.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow12" id="BPMNEdge_flow12">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="751.0" y="222.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="810.0" y="197.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow13" id="BPMNEdge_flow13">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="150.0" y="337.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="510.0" y="325.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow14" id="BPMNEdge_flow14">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="35.0" y="197.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="85.0" y="203.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
            <bpmndi:BPMNEdge bpmnElement="flow15" id="BPMNEdge_flow15">
                <omgdi:waypoint x="137.0" y="231.0"/>
                <omgdi:waypoint x="97.0" y="310.0"/>
            </bpmndi:BPMNEdge>
        </bpmndi:BPMNPlane>
    </bpmndi:BPMNDiagram>
</definitions>
